name: Riffel Lake Reflection
description:
8"x12" / 20x30.5cm
(there is a bigger one as an opion)
please contact me for more options (size/price) 

photo by melanie blaser
http://www.melanieblaser.ch
printed and produced by plywerk.com

Specs:

Print: C-type on Fuji Crystal Archive Paper  Not quite matte and not quite glossy. Lustre (also referred to as Satin) has excellent color saturation without the "sheen" that can be a hinderance in glossy print finishes.

Panel: Plywerk (www.plywerk.com) are 3/4" carbonized vertical grain bamboo and utilize a keyhole slot on the back for easy hanging. The bamboo is sustainably grown and harvested. A transparent PH neutral adhesive binds the print to the bamboo and protects the image from the natural acids in the wood. For more product images visit: http://www.flickr.com/photos/plywerk/sets/72157614121003158
